title: Ep. - 229 - UNSOLVED MYSTERIES
description:
In this episode Kate and Jen discuss six unsolved mystery cases involving the deaths of Lindsay Buziak, Kyron Horman, and the Savopolous family, and the disappearances of 7-year-old Joshua “JJ” Vallow and 17-year-old Tylee Ryan, Brian Shaffer and Jennifer Dulos.
